author: TED
description:
In a tour de force set, multidisciplinary artist and composer Samora Pinderhughes performs four moving songs — “Tongues,” “Gatsby,” “Masculinity” and “Process/Forgive Yourself” — accompanied by Elena Pinderhughes on flute, Elliott Skinner on guitar and The Healing Project Choir. (Recorded at TED2025 on April 10, 2025)
